ces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生活好唔定時 可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係，有時訓唔到，有時訓好多<br />\n唔定時係咩原因？"},{"pid":"c384f47a7bb20b0ff528331a903f92d41f97e694","tid":204130,"uid":74388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:06:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Set 鬧鐘提自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生活好唔定時 可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係，有時訓唔到，有時訓好多<br />\n唔定時係咩原因？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n離不開都係起身時間一時一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a688198626398e68e5d3b36d4a8cc804ce5f37","tid":204130,"uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:09:18.000Z","msg":"醒左就訓唔返？"},{"pid":"599eb7f7e8f6a60a66adfc94b85fbfc7ed9fc158","tid":204130,"uid":74388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醒左就訓唔返？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n朝早可以瘋狂瞓 兩個鐘醒一醒咁<br />\n夜晚一係就瘋狂扎醒 一係就醒咗等天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9295a63d98e78a337eec677a54de5a17b9807dcb","tid":204130,"uid":88303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:13:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人成日都有技不如人嘅感覺 然後就無限自卑<br />\nEveryone is unique 天外有天 依啲bullshit自己都識同自己講<br />\n但都係跳唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來唔係得我一個咁諗自己 <br />\nBtw我知我缺點 靠努力點都解決到 但我成日冇動力 個人又成日好攰 揾唔到solution"},{"pid":"33478081033d47465afd9315dd0fa3f59dd08809","tid":204130,"uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>醒左就訓唔返？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n朝早可以瘋狂瞓 兩個鐘醒一醒咁<br />\n夜晚一係就瘋狂扎醒 一係就醒咗等天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係夜晩訓教有幻覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日覺得間房有人同埋扎醒郁唔到仲見到人影聽到電視機聲"},{"pid":"d814551ee3d48a9072c6990dd4295653b8d3b1c1","tid":204130,"uid":74388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:17:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇人成日都有技不如人嘅感覺 然後就無限自卑<br />\nEveryone is unique 天外有天 依啲bullshit自己都識同自己講<br />\n但都係跳唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來唔係得我一個咁諗自己 <br />\nBtw我知我缺點 靠努力點都解決到 但我成日冇動力 個人又成日好攰 揾唔到solution</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知自己肥又晚晚撈麵 又唔肯做返gym<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e29d78cb10657fc47360de0fdb678ee845ff9b5","tid":204130,"uid":74388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:19:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>醒左就訓唔返？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n朝早可以瘋狂瞓 兩個鐘醒一醒咁<br />\n夜晚一係就瘋狂扎醒 一係就醒咗等天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係夜晩訓教有幻覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日覺得間房有人同埋扎醒郁唔到仲見到人影聽到電視機聲</blockquote><br />\n只係試過覺得有人 不過冇理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8fc89e05adee0df42dc8080dab7fc36df4dffe","tid":204130,"uid":16767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:19:21.000Z","msg":"當初點知自己有呢個病?"},{"pid":"718f04658af6edfc742bf0961d50e7578540d093","tid":204130,"uid":74388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當初點知自己有呢個病?</blockquote><br />\n我算好彩 初期已經識搵社工轉介<br />\n過程唔太記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e60816dc83ca549a07798396fd8fcc90969a8c9","tid":204130,"uid":106742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:23:23.000Z","msg":"抑鬱同焦慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲睇緊醫生 但成日唔想／唔記得食藥<br />\nsee break無paper趕又開始發作"},{"pid":"beae1d583ec4d7b7caaa67ebd92b9ffbfea16331","tid":204130,"uid":53682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人成日都有技不如人嘅感覺 然後就無限自卑<br />\nEveryone is unique 天外有天 依啲bullshit自己都識同自己講<br />\n但都係跳唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來唔係得我一個咁諗自己 <br />\nBtw我知我缺點 靠努力點都解決到 但我成日冇動力 個人又成日好攰 揾唔到solution</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知自己肥又晚晚撈麵 又唔肯做返gym<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打以前有做開gym 應該唔會差得去邊㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a82e280472199e1f2047a21bc68b2ef5363a140","tid":204130,"uid":74388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:26:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抑鬱同焦慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲睇緊醫生 但成日唔想／唔記得食藥<br />\nsee break無paper趕又開始發作</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日要靠搵嘢做先麻醉到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdc8b5d9673d5f64a8c8e80ffda026bec9e1ad2","tid":204130,"uid":74388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有冇人成日都有技不如人嘅感覺 然後就無限自卑<br />\nEveryone is unique 天外有天 依啲bullshit自己都識同自己講<br />\n但都係跳唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來唔係得我一個咁諗自己 <br />\nBtw我知我缺點 靠努力點都解決到 但我成日冇動力 個人又成日好攰 揾唔到solution</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知自己肥又晚晚撈麵 又唔肯做返gym<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打以前有做開gym 應該唔會差得去邊㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人矮 咩都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ac56f503c7b5b4d08c48d41f3c3ee97adcdbf9","tid":204130,"uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>醒左就訓唔返？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n朝早可以瘋狂瞓 兩個鐘醒一醒咁<br />\n夜晚一係就瘋狂扎醒 一係就醒咗等天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係夜晩訓教有幻覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日覺得間房有人同埋扎醒郁唔到仲見到人影聽到電視機聲</blockquote><br />\n只係試過覺得有人 不過冇理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下同醫生講夜晚訓得唔好，佢可能會加多啲鎮定劑or安眠藥"},{"pid":"9e168f3efc146cd80563f8b6f7e8b0e5041b29ba","tid":204130,"uid":106742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:28:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>抑鬱同焦慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲睇緊醫生 但成日唔想／唔記得食藥<br />\nsee break無paper趕又開始發作</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日要靠搵嘢做先麻醉到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我已經將黎緊每一日都砌滿晒<br />\n但<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢一爆出黎 咩都禁唔住 成腦都勁負面<br />\n然後身邊既人都覺得我無食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d19c44857addc56720008ddc941b272647d1815","tid":204130,"uid":106742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>醒左就訓唔返？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n朝早可以瘋狂瞓 兩個鐘醒一醒咁<br />\n夜晚一係就瘋狂扎醒 一係就醒咗等天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係夜晩訓教有幻覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日覺得間房有人同埋扎醒郁唔到仲見到人影聽到電視機聲</blockquote><br />\n只係試過覺得有人 不過冇理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下同醫生講夜晚訓得唔好，佢可能會加多啲鎮定劑or安眠藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我早排都試過 跟住醫生開左安眠藥比我<br />\n我到呢家一唔食就訓唔到 好依賴隻藥 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79777e9f8ddb256a53ce84fe6f6ce0f8cba81468","tid":204130,"uid":74388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T19:31:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>醒